{"tid":2417262,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國逾1750萬人完成注射首劑疫苗，官員稱確診下降！","createTime":"2021-02-21T17:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T19:20:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2dbe8c0a278ede0c6561494cb2004c78a1c963be","tid":2417262,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:31:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576713-20210222.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576713-20210222.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDYw5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=253f1843\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576713-20210222.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4db9d1ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576713-20210222.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國至今有超過1750萬人，完成接種第一劑新型冠狀病毒疫苗，61萬人完成接種第二劑。另外，過去一日新增9800多人確診，215人死亡，數據顯示，新增確診及死亡的人數正在下跌。<br />\n<br />\n首相約翰遜期望在7月中，完成對所有成年人的首劑疫苗接種，較原先預計在9月為早，約翰遜將於當地星期一與內閣高層舉行會議，研究逐步解除封城的路線圖。<br />\n<br />\n衛生大臣夏國賢表示，現時平均每3名成人當中，已有1人完成接種，隨著接種疫苗人數增加，感染情況減少，需要入院治療的人數較第一波疫情大幅減少。"},{"pid":"e6071bbd4e5fa6f8d013393bfbe9b647a107cfaf","tid":2417262,"uid":130079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:35:34.000Z","msg":"Make uk great<br />\nMake uk great again"},{"pid":"a293bb2c511c3ca658727b8cbe9cb77a7a451d5e","tid":2417262,"uid":384590,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:37:33.000Z","msg":"Nooooooooooooooo"},{"pid":"84dd470602eb893645edc61be7806c799839e30a","tid":2417262,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210129/431812662502887424824071.jpeg/OVh7IIfyS27pWSZ_HIz6TyH9-v6d1byVtetAxrXrQMY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2